sentences.english: Eric Schenk had the idea of adding something to the client's initial sequence number.

sentences.english: The UDID is a long string of alphanumeric characters which will appear in place of the serial number.
sentences.chinese: UDID是出现在序列号内的一长串文字数字式字符。

sentences.english: Please check your information and re-enter your serial number .
sentences.chinese: 请检查您的信息并重新输入您的序列号。

sentences.english: Start the keygen and generate a serial.
sentences.chinese: 这个序列号的话，产生一种开始。

sentences.english: Each node is assigned a unique identifying serial number.
sentences.chinese: 每个节点都指定了一个惟一的标识序列号。

sentences.english: Every edition of textbook will be revised periodically with the edition serial number.
sentences.chinese: 每册定期更新升级新版本，各有版本序列号。

sentences.english: For example, assume that this parameter is set to 4, and that you currently have four cached sequences.
sentences.chinese: 如果我连续插入记录，那么序列号是排序是正常的。

sentences.english: If the serial number is valid, certificate details will display.
sentences.chinese: 如果序列号有效，将显示证书详细信息。

sentences.english: Item and serial numbers are printed on the warning label located in the non-inflation area of the buoyancy compensator.
sentences.chinese: 条款和序列号印在浮力补给装置的标签上。

sentences.english: The temporal reference is defined by an image number.
sentences.chinese: 时域睥参考由图像序列号决定。

sentences.english: The LSA with the higher(newer)sequence number is more recent.
sentences.chinese: 拥有最高序列号的LSA是最新的。

sentences.english: It is on the periodic table of elements under the symbol Bi at atomic number 83.
sentences.chinese: 在元素周期表里序列号是83，标志是BI。
